description.raw:
Checking CI

* Update MOI and MassMatrix documentation

* Updating documentation

* Move documentation to non-deprecated function

* Update documentation to Inertial::Pose

* Review updates

* Added link about notation

* new gtest on ign-math2 to fix windows compiler warnings

* try to fix some signed-unsigned mismatch windows warnings (C4389)

* one more unsigned fix

* Close branch new_gtest_2

* Close branch new_gtest_2_unsigned

* remove old gtest diff

* Set cxx standard for gtest

* Close branch merge34

* Close branch inertia_doc_update

* set c++standard variable in root CMakeLists.txt

* Close branch merge45
